dc_title_s: C-12 Geologic atlas of Goodhue County, Minnesota [Part A]
dc_description_s: 6 pls. Scale 1:100,000. Pl. 1, data-base; pl. 2, bedrock geology; pl. 3, surficial geology and thickness of Quaternary sediments; pl. 4, Quaternary stratigraphy; pl. 5, bedrock topography; pl. 6, geologic resources. Part B Published separately by the Minnesota Department of Natural Resources, Division of Waters. Supplementary files include ArcGis coverages, shapefiles and/or ESRI grids used to construct the plates, and metadata.
